metadata.name: Memory Moon
metadata.description:
Memory is an invaluable treasure that makes eternal what would otherwise be ephemeral. It is the portal through which we access our past and the key to unlock our future. Don't let anyone take it away from you, don't let it blow away. 
It's not about the moon, it’s about the idea behind the moon. This is the reason art matters.


1120 × 1120 px, 60 fps, H.264, audio AAC 48KHz, 35 seconds loop.
Unique Edition
